GreenHopper allows user to group issues into sprints. Enable 'Sprint' Custom Field for CSV import.

h3. Issue Summary
Comment not added with Jira API transition Issue v3

h3. Steps to Reproduce
# Call the Jira Cloud REST API v3 endpoint to [Transition issue|https://developer.atlassian.com/cloud/jira/platform/rest/v3/#api-rest-api-3-issue-issueIdOrKey-transitions-post]
# The payload is correctly populated
{code:java}
...
"update": {
    "comment": [
      {
        "add": {
          "body": {
            "type": "doc",
            "version": 1,
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Bug has been fixed",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  },
...
{code}

h3. Expected Results
 * Comment should be added into the ticket when transitioned

h3. Actual Results
 * Comment not added into the ticket when transitioned

h3. Workaround
 * Use the v2 of [Transition issue|https://developer.atlassian.com/cloud/jira/platform/rest/v2/#api-rest-api-2-issue-issueIdOrKey-transitions-post].
